        <updateDate>2020-06-12T13:43:25Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Workforce Investment Disclosure Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill requires an issuer of securities to disclose certain information regarding human capital management policies, practices, and performance. This information includes workforce data related to </p> <ul> <li>full-time, part-time, and contingent employees; </li> <li>turnover and retention rates; </li> <li>racial, ethnic, and gender composition; </li> <li>skills, training, and capabilities; </li> <li>health and safety; </li> <li>compensation and incentives; and </li> <li>recruiting. </li> </ul>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
